WEBVTT

00:00:01.992 --> 00:00:03.714
Yes, it's dark.

00:00:04.968 --> 00:00:08.397
I'm wondering how long
we can all stand it

00:00:08.421 --> 00:00:13.194
without picking up our phone
and turning the flashlights on.

00:00:13.847 --> 00:00:14.997
Seconds?

00:00:15.689 --> 00:00:16.895
Minutes?

00:00:17.276 --> 00:00:18.426
A whole hour?

00:00:21.768 --> 00:00:25.566
Don't worry, I'm not going to give you
my whole speech in the dark.

00:00:26.606 --> 00:00:28.673
But it's something I'm used to.

00:00:29.146 --> 00:00:34.344
For more than 10 years,
I and two million people back home